jminusminus

Class Member

  • java.lang.Object
    • jminusminus.Member
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Constructor, Field, Method

    abstract class Member
extends Object
    A wrapper for members (eg Fields, Methods, Constructors) in the Java API. Members are used in message expressions, field selections, and new object construction operations.
